   "source": [
    "# 03｜4Pi-Confocal 与 Richards-Wolf 参考解工作流（中文）\n",
    "\n",
    "本 notebook 目标：\n",
    "1. 演示 4Pi 相位扫描；\n",
    "2. 演示双臂不平衡与像差；\n",
    "3. 用 Debye 参考解做小网格对照。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "622c3118",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "3.12.12 | packaged by conda-forge | (main, Jan 26 2026, 23:38:32) [MSC v.1944 64 bit (AMD64)]\n",
      "当前 sys.path 的前两个路径: ['F:\\\\4pi-instant-SIM\\\\4Pi-iSIM Adaptive Optics\\\\AO-26\\\\pyotf-vector', 'f:\\\\4pi-instant-SIM\\\\4Pi-iSIM Adaptive Optics\\\\AO-26\\\\.conda\\\\python312.zip']\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "import sys\n",
    "print(sys.version)\n",
    "project_root = r'F:\\4pi-instant-SIM\\4Pi-iSIM Adaptive Optics\\AO-26\\pyotf-vector'\n",
    "if project_root not in sys.path:\n",
    "    sys.path.insert(0, project_root)\n",
    "print(f\"当前 sys.path 的前两个路径: {sys.path[:2]}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "9cb6ca66",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif'] = ['Microsoft YaHei']  # 指定默认字体\n",
    "plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False  # 解决负号'-'显示异常的问题\n",
    "from pyotf.microscope import FourPiConfocalMicroscope\n",
    "from pyotf.vector import richards_wolf_linearly_polarized_psf"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "53bf3f5e",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 第 1 步：创建 4Pi 模型"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "id": "ef4f1e98",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "PSF shape: (64, 64, 64)\n",
      "PSF sum: 0.9999999999999998\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "ef4f1e98",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "base_kwargs = dict(model=\"hanser\", na=1.1, ni=1.33, wl=520, size=64, pixel_size=80, oversample_factor=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "model_4pi = FourPiConfocalMicroscope(\n",
    "    wl_exc=488,\n",
    "    pinhole_size=0.8,\n",
    "    phase_exc=0.0,\n",
    "    phase_det=0.0,\n",
    "    amp_ratio_exc=0.9,\n",
    "    amp_ratio_det=1.1,\n",
    "    aberrations_exc_arm2={\"vertical coma\": 0.12},\n",
    "    aberrations_det_arm1={\"oblique astigmatism\": 0.08},\n",
    "    **base_kwargs\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"PSF shape:\", model_4pi.PSF.shape)\n",
    "print(\"PSF sum:\", model_4pi.PSF.sum())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "c793c9b7",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 第 2 步：做相位扫描（phase_scan）\n",
    "\n",
    "观察相位变化对轴向响应的影响。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "id": "a1d86d99",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "stack shape: (7, 64, 64, 64)\n"
     ]
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 700x400 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "phases = np.linspace(0, 0.5*np.pi, 7)\n",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "a1d86d99",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "phases = np.linspace(0, 2*np.pi, 7)\n",
    "stack = model_4pi.phase_scan(phases, channel=\"both\")\n",
    "print(\"stack shape:\", stack.shape)\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(7,4))\n",
    "for i, p in enumerate(phases):\n",
    "    prof = stack[i].sum(axis=(1,2))\n",
    "    plt.plot(prof, label=f\"{p:.2f}\")\n",
    "plt.title(\"4Pi 相位扫描：轴向积分曲线\")\n",
    "plt.xlabel(\"z index\")\n",
    "plt.ylabel(\"integrated intensity\")\n",
    "plt.legend(ncol=2, fontsize=8)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "7340db31",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 第 3 步：Richards-Wolf 参考解（小网格）\n",
    "\n",
    "注意：这个计算会比 FFT 路线慢很多。建议先用小网格。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "id": "4dbe74db",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "RW PSF shape: (11, 21, 21)\n",
      "RW PSF sum: 1.0\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "4dbe74db",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "x = np.linspace(-200, 200, 21)\n",
    "y = np.linspace(-200, 200, 21)\n",
    "z = np.linspace(-300, 300, 11)\n",
    "\n",
    "psf_rw = richards_wolf_linearly_polarized_psf(\n",
    "    wl=520, na=1.1, ni=1.33, x=x, y=y, z=z, n_theta=40, n_phi=64\n",
    ")\n",
    "print(\"RW PSF shape:\", psf_rw.shape)\n",
    "print(\"RW PSF sum:\", psf_rw.sum())"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ad4c9925",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 第 4 步：看参考解中心切片"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 10,
   "id": "11f951f0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 500x400 with 2 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "11f951f0",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "z0 = psf_rw.shape[0] // 2\n",
    "plt.figure(figsize=(5,4))\n",
    "plt.imshow(psf_rw[z0], cmap=\"viridis\")\n",
    "plt.title(\"Richards-Wolf 参考解中心切片\")\n",
    "plt.colorbar()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "624abcad",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 练习建议\n",
    "\n",
    "1. 把 `n_theta` / `n_phi` 调大，观察耗时和图像稳定性；\n",
    "2. 给 `richards_wolf_linearly_polarized_psf` 增加 `pcoefs`，观察像差效应；\n",
    "3. 对比 4Pi 模型与参考解的轴向 profile 趋势。"
   ]
  }
